Son restos de pintura,
de pigmento.

01:09:47.580 --> 01:09:50.440
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: So, he has
leftover pigment and paint

01:09:50.440 --> 01:09:53.010
that he uses also for the box.

01:09:53.010 --> 01:09:56.340
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez: Este es
el poema uno de los versos

