01:12:36.670 --> 01:12:38.650
about his artistic life.

01:12:38.650 --> 01:12:39.950
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez:

01:12:39.950 --> 01:12:42.430
Me he dedicado por muchos
años a la enseñanza del arte.

01:12:42.430 --> 01:12:45.020
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: He spent
many years teaching art.

01:12:45.020 --> 01:12:47.880
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez: Me dediqué
por más de 35 años al mundo del

01:12:47.880 --> 01:12:51.760
diseño de escenografía y
vestuario y luces en el teatro.

01:12:51.760 --> 01:12:54.010
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: For more than
35 years, he was involved

01:12:54.010 --> 01:12:55.500
in theater set design,

01:12:55.500 --> 01:12:58.780
and costume design,
and lighting design.

01:12:58.780 --> 01:13:02.770
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez: Pinto,
dibujo, escribe poesía.

01:13:02.770 --> 01:13:05.640
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: He paints,
he draws, he writes poems.

01:13:05.640 --> 01:13:07.820
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez: Pero de
todas las cosas que hago,

01:13:07.820 --> 01:13:10.510
lo que yo quiero hacer hasta
el día que me muera son

01:13:10.510 --> 01:13:11.810
estos libros.

01:13:11.810 --> 01:13:13.280
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: But of all
the things that he does,

01:13:13.280 --> 01:13:15.670
what he wants to do until
the day he dies is this.

01:13:15.670 --> 01:13:16.970
&gt;&gt; Rolando Estévez:
Estos libros.

01:13:16.970 --> 01:13:18.270
Gracias.

01:13:18.270 --> 01:13:19.570
&gt;&gt; Ruth Behar: These books.

01:13:19.570 --> 01:13:20.870
Thank you.

