01:19:21.290 --> 01:19:24.460
&gt;&gt; Hi, and thak you,
Estévez, gracias.

01:19:24.460 --> 01:19:26.740
Incredible, it's beautiful.

01:19:26.740 --> 01:19:28.930
I've arounf three questions.

