01:20:32.920 --> 01:20:36.900
&gt;&gt; So, the glue or the
adhesive, there's a --

01:20:39.210 --> 01:20:46.550
The adhesive is of a variety
and by keeping materials

01:20:46.550 --> 01:20:49.490
in the closed boxes,
number one, in the dark,

01:20:49.490 --> 01:20:51.850
and also in a controlled
environment,

01:20:51.850 --> 01:20:54.430
we control the humidity
and the temperature,

01:20:54.430 --> 01:20:59.760
the cooler the temperature, the
slower the chemical reaction,

01:20:59.760 --> 01:21:04.890
and so the adhesive,
in fact, will work.

01:21:04.890 --> 01:21:06.190
Oh, sorry, sorry.

01:21:06.190 --> 01:21:11.560
So, the adhesive will be
preserved for a period of time.

01:21:11.560 --> 01:21:17.760
One of the other things is when
various people go down to Cuba,

01:21:17.760 --> 01:21:22.260
myself included, we take
good adhesive down assured.

01:21:22.260 --> 01:21:26.680
So, I did that when I
went down in the 90s

01:21:26.680 --> 01:21:32.370
and in the early 2000s, to take
adhesive down to enable them

01:21:32.370 --> 01:21:36.530
to be able to make
more of the books.

01:21:36.530 --> 01:21:40.190
So, I think that answers
